## Description {#details}

A cache of @llvm.assume calls within a function.

This cache provides fast lookup of assumptions within a function by caching them and amortizing the cost of scanning for them across all queries. Passes that create new assumptions are required to call <a href="#a23187618f079555e127ba0e7b4581530">registerAssumption()</a> to register any new @llvm.assume calls that they create. Deletions of @llvm.assume calls do not require special handling.
